ttp_template:
<group name="adjacency_type_interface_next_hop_route_entry">
  Adjacency Type: {{ADJACENCY_TYPE | ORPHRASE}}
Route Entry: {{ROUTE_ENTRY | ORPHRASE}}
  Interface: {{INTERFACE | ORPHRASE}}
  Next Hop: {{NEXT_HOP | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
Forwarding Components:
  Adjacency Information

Route Entry: 192.168.1.0/24
  Interface: GigabitEthernet1
  Next Hop: 10.0.0.2
  Adjacency Type: ARP

Route Entry: 172.16.0.0/16
  Interface: GigabitEthernet2
  Next Hop: 10.0.1.2
  Adjacency Type: ARP

Route Entry: 10.0.0.0/8
  Interface: GigabitEthernet3
  Next Hop: 10.0.2.2
  Adjacency Type: L2

Route Entry: 192.168.2.0/24
  Interface: GigabitEthernet4
  Next Hop: 10.0.3.2
  Adjacency Type: ARP
textfsm_template:
Value ROUTE_ENTRY (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+/\d+)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value NEXT_HOP (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)
Value ADJACENCY_TYPE (\S+)

Start
  ^Route Entry: ${ROUTE_ENTRY}\s*$$
  ^\s*Interface: ${INTERFACE}\s*$$
  ^\s*Next Hop: ${NEXT_HOP}\s*$$
  ^\s*Adjacency Type: ${ADJACENCY_TYPE}\s*$$ -> Record
